  "texts": [
    "1,872 publications extracted from the Web of Sciences.",
    "Key domain expressions (nodes in the map) were extracted by means of text mining on the title and abstracts of these documents.",
    "The semantic proximity between these expressions was calculated as the metric confidence, i.e.",
    "the maximum of the two conditional probabilities of having one expression knowing the other in the same publication.",
    "The resulting graph was visualized using Gephi."
  ],
